{"tid":663264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［戲院座位討論］港共01抄完post同借'網民'把口串鳩連登仔","createTime":"2018-05-13T07:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T07:44:40.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4da4fb7142b838180700a528fe2f05217678f97","tid":663264,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/145745_3eb7aac83ed1ea3c96e297885a05459a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F145745_3eb7aac83ed1ea3c96e297885a05459a.png&h=103b296f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯⋯雖然有部分網民支持樓主，認為這種買法影響他人，<strong>不過有不少人反指摘樓主的想法更自私，形容「先到先得都係競爭」，買電影票向來如此，着樓主「自己包場睇」，就算刻意隔開座位也無犯法。</strong>另有網民留言，指如果想和女朋友看電影應該盡早買票，如果對他們買票手法不滿，大可買「單丁」座位入場，與對方當面對質，籲不要只做「鍵盤戰士」。樓主回應指自己會買飛入場找那兩人，並斷言對方是「死MK」。網民又提議樓主買下兩個「單丁位」，再隔着兩人不停傳爆谷。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，有相信會自己一個看電影的網民留言，指「靠佢哋先可以遲買都有得執下呢啲唔錯嘅單丁位」。同時，有留言指樓主根本不能確定是有兩人隔「單丁位」買連座，因為有機會兩人很早就買下戲票，買連座時隔空了兩個座位，但有人買了其中一個，最後才變成留下「單丁位」。又有人留意到，該座位表的前排「ABCD」明明有大堆座位，只是樓主選不到較好的座位就發文鬧人。⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/187526/睇戲買連座隔出-單丁位-連登仔發文轟自私-網民-先到先得?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C%2F187526%2F%E7%9D%87%E6%88%B2%E8%B2%B7%E9%80%A3%E5%BA%A7%E9%9A%94%E5%87%BA-%E5%96%AE%E4%B8%81%E4%BD%8D-%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB%E4%BB%94%E7%99%BC%E6%96%87%E8%BD%9F%E8%87%AA%E7%A7%81-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E5%85%88%E5%88%B0%E5%85%88%E5%BE%97%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=I4UYGyOFC9GC9oh4YvWiijPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d79f86c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/187526/睇戲買連座隔出-單丁位-連登仔發文轟自私-網民-先到先得?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama</a><br />\n<br />\n明明都喺連登留言，點解開post就喺連登仔，寫回覆就網民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n標籤連登仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有你老味抄post抄到逐個留言cap圖，咁樣填滿啲版位，懶撚到閪"},{"pid":"0ccb3d01bdfb792edb1ce968a9204eb1e436efe2","tid":663264,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:06:43.000Z","msg":"共業啦共業啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連狗及其爪牙喜聞樂見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d097bfc44b19bf08f29b13ec125228f93cd996b9","tid":663264,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0ccb3d01bdfb792edb1ce968a9204eb1e436efe2","tid":663264,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:06:43.000Z","msg":"共業啦共業啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連狗及其爪牙喜聞樂見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"回家了"}]}